title: McGuire
description: ***“McGuire”*** is a bold, tongue-in-cheek response to rumors and assumptions about Miycho’s preferences. With **confident** delivery and playful energy, the track flips outside **commentary** into self-expression, asserting individuality and control over the narrative. It’s unapologetic, **catchy**, and rooted in reclaiming the story on Miycho’s own terms.
